list.name: Default
list.comment: Enabled SASS for application files. Moved button bar scss to it's own file.

task.summary: Added basic user registration with error message.

Each state now resolves the user authentication. If not authenticated, it will change to login state. Fixed controllers to not use a rootscope user object and use the Auth service for getting uid. Fixed add item to use Auth for UID.

Added error directive to show errors on registration and login page. Moved container crud operations to data service. Added removeAllItems method to trash expired items. Fixed bug where 'trash' button label didn't show on expired items. Added basic container init for new users. Fixed count of expired items in stat pie graph. Fixed init of the logging service.
Added missing files for form error. Missing file for trash all fix. Hide add item button on login and registration pages.
Changed add icon to have a circle around the plus sign to improve visiblity.
Fixed logout / login data reference issues. Fixed missing ios icons for building for ios.
Added a button bar to each item that is activated by clicking an item. Added remove, trash, extend, and use functionality to items in the expiring view.
Updated visual design of items view and bottom toolbar.
Reduced text size of item title. Reduced text size of expiration date. Removed 'Tomorrow' date and replaced it with day of the week.
Fixed bug where tomorrow was showing as a date instead of a day of the week.
Added button bar animation to the item. Modified gulp file to watch for css changes (temporarily). Refactored vendor files structure.
Enabled SASS for application files. Moved button bar and item scss to it's own file.
Added item edit functionality. Moved addItem() method to data service. Added updateItem method to data service. Placed inline form lables for add form.
